data.description: Adorable one-story Bixby home on nearly 1/2 acre with 4 beds, 2 bath and 2 living areas. Property is adorned with large pecan trees and large backyard. No HOA! Great spacious layout with the Den/second living area that's great for entertaining. Spacious laundry room. Remodeled around 3 years ago with new paint, new flooring in main rooms, updated lighting, granite in kitchen, and new water heater. Roof is about 4 years old along with energy efficient windows. The master is oversized with a large walk in closet and private bathroom. Close proximity to schools and quiet neighborhood. Closer to 2,300 sqft. It is in flood zone but seller has never had any issues and indicates flood insurance premium is approximately $700 annually
